title: The Horse with the Flying Tail [1960 - USA] Walt Disney
description:
The Horse with the Flying Tail (1960 - USA)

Family / Documentary
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0054993/


Academy Awards Oscar - Won - Best Documentary Feature

A palomino horse born into poverty is given a chance to compete in what he loves best, jumping and soaring over hurdles. Trained by an ex-cavalry officer who recognizes his ability, the horse endures a tough and bumpy progress to win the world famous King George V Cup. This is the true story of Nautical, the star jumper of the United States Equestrian Team.
